     C                   PARM                    ZField                                       CAS006
     C                   PARM                    ZADec                                        CAS006
     C                   MOVE      ZField        SNTCR                                        CAS006
     C                   ENDIF                                                                CAS006
     C                   ENDIF                                                                CAS006
